{
  "name": "Hear Name",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/divination.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Divination sphere, caster level 5th.</p>\n<p>You may spend a spell point to hear your name or another specific phrase of your choice whenever it is mentioned. When you activate this sense, designate a word, phrase, or name. If a creature within 1 mile per caster level of you uses that word, phrase, or name to refer to you or an action in relation to you (such as attacking your base or intent to find something that belongs to you), you immediately hear the rest of the sentence in which they used the word, phrase, or name. You may dismiss this sense to learn the speaker&#8217;s name, appearance, and location.</p>\n",
